text: Antoine Pierre Schildwein (10 August 1911 - 24 September 1995) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1995 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sarreguemines
